    <item>
      <title>伊拉克在关于浮动气码头的会谈中，以弥合电源差距</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/iraq-in-talks-over-floating-gas-terminals-to-bridge-power-gap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊拉克正在与几家公司进行会谈，以便在6月初之前确保两个浮动存储重新设备，因为欧佩克的第二大生产商试图解决由美国对伊朗的举动造成的电力短缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/iraq-in-talks-over-floating-gas-terminals-to-bridge-power-gap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 23:37:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场开始时，石油稳定为特朗普的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-24</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在本周开始时，石油稳定，因为交易者权衡了更多的美国关税和即将推动的欧佩克+供应量的后果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-24</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 23:28:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
